DryadDataFile.dcterms:title: Male Annual Reproductive Success Data
DryadDataFile.dcterms:description: This file contains data required for the analyses of male annual reproductive success in relation to the male's mean kinship with the socially-paired females with which he made each breeding attempt across his lifetime. This analysis is presented in the paper's Supporting Information.
